    Fix Windows event loop error and add MQTT credentials
    
    Replace aiohttp with asyncio.to_thread + urllib.request in Tasmota
    driver and MPC-HC backend. qasync 0.28 on Windows wraps ProactorEventLoop
    which doesn't implement add_reader/add_writer; urllib runs in a thread
    pool and bypasses the issue entirely. Also removes aiohttp dependency.
    
    Add username/password fields to MqttOutputConfig, wired through config
    serialization, aiomqtt client construction, and the output dialog
    (password field uses masked echo mode).
    
