    Initial implementation of funscript-gateway
    
    Bridge service connecting video players (HereSphere, MPC-HC) to smart
    home outputs (Tasmota, MQTT) via funscript haptic axis data. Includes
    full async architecture (asyncio + qasync + PySide6), threshold signal
    processor with hysteresis, configurable per-output behavior for pause,
    disconnect, and missing-axis states, system tray UI, and PyInstaller
    build script.
    
